\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
Proof of the expression for 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{CF}$
\end_inset

 in Proposition 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "prop:The-asymptotic-variances"
plural "false"
